* Fri May 12 2017 17:54:40 +0530 mbhangui@gmail.com 2.2-1.1%{?dist}
Release 2.2 Start 08/05/2017
10/05/2011
1.  use packetsize > 512 to avoid dkim failures for sites having long txt
    records (hotmail.com)
2.  config-fast removed display of DESTDIR
11/05/2017
3.  svscanboot/svscan option run .svscan/run or INITCMD. Use unshare --mount
    option to mount private mounts like custom resolv.conf
4.  svscan - run .svscan/shutdown on SIGTERM
5.  added inotify program to get file system events
